# X/Twitter API Configuration
# Choose ONE of the following authentication methods:

# Option 1: Bearer Token (Recommended for read-only access)
# Get your Bearer Token from https://developer.twitter.com/en/portal/dashboard
X_BEARER_TOKEN=your_twitter_api_bearer_token_here

# Option 2: API Key and Secret (Alternative authentication method)
# Get your API credentials from https://developer.twitter.com/en/portal/dashboard
# X_API_KEY=your_twitter_api_consumer_key_here
# X_API_SECRET=your_twitter_api_consumer_secret_here

# Priority: If both methods are configured, X_BEARER_TOKEN takes precedence